4. Calculate according to the mathematical expectation formula $EX=\sum_{i=0}^{3}i×P(X=i)$, substitute the data to get $EX=0× rac{3}{20}+1× rac{8}{20}+2× rac{7}{20}+3× rac{2}{20}= rac{7}{5}$.

